author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at "Ready or Not", a game that means a lot to me since it's one of the few horror-tactical games on the market that actually treats it's audience like adults. With it coming to consoles it seems some censorship is due despite years of never compromising on vision. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The Censorship of Ready Or Not...
